OL,3,CCities launch 'cool spaces' to escape
OL,4,Cthe heat - where can I find them?
OL,6,FAs the UK swelters through its third
OL,7,Fheatwave of the year, councils are
OL,8,Foffering "cool spaces" for people
OL,9,Fneeding to escape the heat.
OL,11,FCities delivering this service include
OL,12,FBath and Somerset, Birmingham,
OL,13,FBristol, Leeds, London, Manchester,
OL,14,Fand Rochdale.
OL,16,FBut what is a "cool space" and where
OL,17,Fcan you find them? ITV News explains.
OL,19,FWhat is a cool space?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
