OL,3,CCities launch 'cool spaces' to escape
OL,4,Cthe heat - where can I find them?
OL,6,FA cool space is a building that offers
OL,7,Ffree water, shelter, and rest out of
OL,8,Fthe sun. Not all cool spaces have air
OL,9,Fconditioning, and they do not provide
OL,10,Fmedical support.
OL,12,FHowever, they are a space where people
OL,13,Fcan relax and rehydrate.
OL,15,FBath and North East Somerset
OL,17,FIn the last heatwave in late June, the
OL,18,FSouth Western Ambulance Service NHS
OL,19,FFoundation Trust said they received
OL,20,Fthe most demand ever recorded by the
OL,21,Fservice.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
