OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1783671598
OL,3,CCities launch 'cool spaces' to escape
OL,4,Cthe heat - where can I find them?
OL,6,FTo combat this, Bath Sports and
OL,7,FLeisure Centre and Bath Central
OL,8,FLibrary are among centres that have
OL,9,Fopened to the public to provide a cool
OL,10,Fspace for the community.
OL,12,FThe council also provides support via
OL,13,Fa Community Wellbeing Hub, and moved
OL,14,Fbin collections earlier to 6am on
OL,15,FThursday, July 9 and Friday, July 10,
OL,16,Fto help workers in the heat.
OL,18,FThe Church of England Birmingham has
OL,19,Fopened up churches as cool spaces.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
