OL,3,CCities launch 'cool spaces' to escape
OL,4,Cthe heat - where can I find them?
OL,6,FVolunteers gave out ice lollies and
OL,7,Fwater in Summerfield Park and looked
OL,8,Fout for vulnerable members of the
OL,9,Fcommunity.
OL,11,FRevd Katie Stock, said: "We are in the
OL,12,F2% most deprived communities in the
OL,13,Fcountry, so hope is in short supply,
OL,14,Fbut a welcoming smile and an ice lolly
OL,15,Fgoes a long way."
