OL,3,CCities launch 'cool spaces' to escape
OL,4,Cthe heat - where can I find them?
OL,6,FThe Mayor of London has created an
OL,7,Finteractive map showing cool spaces
OL,8,Fwith air conditioning, toilets, and
OL,9,Fdrinking water.
OL,11,FIt's part of Sir Sadiq Khan's Heat
OL,12,FReady London plan, looking at how
OL,13,FLondon communities can adapt to the
OL,14,Fheat.
OL,16,FAge UK Islington is encouraging people
OL,17,Fto stay safe in the heat by
OL,18,Fremembering the acronym DUCKS:
OL,20,FDrink water
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
