OL,3,CCities launch 'cool spaces' to escape
OL,4,Cthe heat - where can I find them?
OL,6,FUse shade/keep cool
OL,8,FCheck on neighbours
OL,10,FKnow the symptoms of heat exhaustion
OL,11,Fand heat stroke
OL,13,FStay in a cool space
OL,15,FManchester City Council has listed 22
OL,16,Flibraries that will open to the public
OL,17,Fas cool spaces to provide shelter
OL,18,Fduring the heatwave.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
