OL,3,CCities launch 'cool spaces' to escape
OL,4,Cthe heat - where can I find them?
OL,6,FRochdale Borough Council also has a
OL,7,Flist of 12 "welcome spaces" at youth
OL,8,Fcentres, libraries and community
OL,9,Fcentres.
OL,11,FThe council said members of the public
OL,12,Fcan "pop in to relax, make use of the
OL,13,Ffacilities, and get a free
OL,14,Frefreshment."
OL,16,FThe NHS advises people to drink plenty
OL,17,Fof water and wear sunscreen.
OL,19,FIf you are feeling unwell, contact
OL,20,F111, or if your symptoms are serious
OL,21,Fring 999.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
